data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom elegantly updated Pool home in desirable SE Cape Coral. This home checks off all of your boxes; 2023 Roof, 2022 Electric Panel, Large pool area oasis with luxury pavers, and higher end appliances and finishes. The first thing you'll notice is the FRESH, modern exterior paint and landscaping giving you excellent curb appeal. Once you enter you will experience the spacious open concept living room that leads directly into the huge kitchen which is perfect for entertaining and gourmet cooking. The kitchen features appliances such as a Samsung Bespoke Fridge, modern range hood and flat top stainless stove. You will love the 24X48 oversized ceramic tile throughout the home and the bathrooms have modern touches such as tile walls and very tasteful fixtures. The icing on the cake is the beautiful outdoor kitchen that has stainless steel appliances, a solid surface countertop, and beautiful dark stone veneer walls. Located minutes from the downtown area with local restaurants, 10 minutes from marinas, waterside restaurants, and shopping. Less than 10 minutes from Publix, Target, Starbucks, and more! Call for a tour today!
